dct_title_s: Plat book of Alcona County, Michigan
dct_description_sm: Abstract: Atlas of township property maps showing names of rural landowners.
Notes: Publication date estimated by M-65 not being labeled. Also, the road slopes down through Lott and Bryant, rather than going straight south to Hale. Additionally, US 23 is not on the map.
